sentence:
(RTTNews) - Below are the earnings highlights for Salesforce.com Inc (CRM):

-Earnings: -$109 million in Q3 vs. $105 million in the same period last year.
-EPS: -$0.12 in Q3 vs. $0.13 in the same period last year.
-Excluding items, Salesforce.com Inc reported adjusted earnings of $667 million or $0.75 per share for the period.
-Analysts projected $0.66 per share -Revenue: $4.51 billion in Q3 vs. $3.39 billion in the same period last year.
